OL,5, Gamblers who are losing #1,000 a day   
OL,6, are expected to face checks as part of 
OL,7, new, tougher gambling regulations.     
OL,9,FSources say these will kick in when a  
OL,10,Fgambler loses #1,000 in 24 hours, or   
OL,11,F#2,000 over 90 days. How these will be 
OL,12,Fcarried out is as yet unclear.         
OL,14,FCulture Secretary Lucy Frazer, who will
OL,15,Foutline the plans in Parliament later, 
OL,16,Fsays the rise of smartphones means "now
OL,17,Fthere's a Las Vegas on every phone".   
OL,19,FMs Frazer said her "balanced" proposal 
OL,20,Fwould still let people enjoy a flutter.
